{"tid":1821362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港地投票] 已達5000用家！","createTime":"2020-01-12T08:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T13:41:39.000Z","uid":162008,"like":78,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"10100247d4270137fedda188203c157af4c20659","tid":1821362,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"熱烈慶祝已達5000用家！<br />\n<br />\n呢個對我地團隊係好大鼓舞，多謝各界（特別係IT手足）。<br />\n百屌成材，有意見我地先可以不斷進步！<br />\n<br />\nIOS已批1.049，重要update如下<br />\n<br />\n- 新增多項措施，保障只限香港境內投票<br />\n- 資料多重加密<br />\n- 加設香港人日程投票選項<br />\n- 增設直接連結分享<br />\n<br />\n- 去大台化 不設user name<br />\n- 人人都可以發起議題<br />\n- 一系列措施去盡力確保一人一票 <br />\n<br />\nAndroid暫時仲係1.042  <br />\n1.049審批中<br />\n<br />\n團隊唔會就甘就停步，我地正準備：<br />\n- 已設立外國server，所有資料將存放於外國<br />\n- 加設18區社區投票選項<br />\n- 新增投票/ 留言/ 回覆 通知功能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持，愈多人用呢個App，先愈有公信力！<br />\n唔介意的話，好評一下或者睇一睇廣告，廣告收入將資助外國server租金及營運。"},{"pid":"5c4d4d9ee91458a56370e7fb53b592fc563a8829","tid":1821362,"uid":162008,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"整呢個App 有幾個目標想做到，  需要大家幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為而家D 風向都令我有D 擔心，又話唔用得TG, 有時又叫停好多野。不過我係度諗，多一個平台可以多一個表達意見既地方，香港而家好在仲未有23 條，資訊流通係我地既優勢（當然如果俾5毛帶風向就好危險）<br />\n<br />\n所以我目標係盡量確保投票既人唔可以重覆（至少唔可以咁容易重覆）就算有5毛， 大家既真實意見都唔會咁易被覆蓋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二樣目標係希望香港人會留意香港有咩議題，就算唔打字討論，可以以用投票表達，當香港人習慣左投票，將來有其他重大事項都會更多人出黎表達意見<br />\n<br />\n第三， 香港人投左區議員出黎，唔應該就咁就算，希望可以令香港人注意自己社區既事項，包括社區建設，屋苑，道路設施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=104a736b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a>"},{"pid":"daee07e49026c59eeb2ed64551e8282465626d7e","tid":1821362,"uid":162008,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J1nNc7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ1nNc7d.jpg&h=7da39cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默，一起發聲，習慣投票表達意見吧<br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下載連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXfrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=104a736b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a>"},{"pid":"d494072205f63b094ab691feba8812c9b79ee8eb","tid":1821362,"uid":252069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">明明好成功,我哋錯咗重點啫,調整心態就得</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820242</a>"},{"pid":"6a041dfd17ba891fdf134a36403de2a96d345fd6","tid":1821362,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1701392d02e1c3443ffd04f8b5399e29c7c8d296","tid":1821362,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"推，   請大家幫手"},{"pid":"d60668c6f3162a910752f0408ef49f09452d29f5","tid":1821362,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce4fa0221a30954a7a908c27df04025d7b4272cb","tid":1821362,"uid":56833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"